            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Specialized in software testing for the hospitality industry,
            including Point of Sale (POS) systems, payment gateways, and room
            scheduling applications.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Intergrupo -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between mb-4">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ebony">Intergrupo (Software One)</h3>
              <p class="text-xl text-red-orange">Sr Quality Engineer</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-gray-600 mt-2 md:mt-0">
              <p>January 2015 - December 2018 (4 years)</p>
              <p class="text-sm">Bogot√° D.C., Colombia</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Worked across healthcare, telecommunications, and finance sectors,
            ensuring quality in complex systems like medical appointment
            applications and data warehouses.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Q-Vision -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between mb-4">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ebony">Q-Vision</h3>
              <p class="text-xl text-red-orange">Test Analyst Intermediate</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-gray-600 mt-2 md:mt-0">
              <p>January 2014 - December 2015 (2 years)</p>
              <p class="text-sm">Bogot√° D.C., Colombia</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Focused on eCommerce platforms, ensuring seamless functionality for
            product search, shopping cart management, and payment gateways.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- BolColombia -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between mb-4">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ebony">BolColombia</h3>
              <p class="text-xl text-red-orange">Software developer .Net - PHP</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-gray-600 mt-2 md:mt-0">
              <p>January 2012 - December 2014 (3 years)</p>
              <p class="text-sm">Bogot√° D.C., Colombia</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Developed web and mobile applications for door-to-door sales
            operations, integrating real-time data collection and order
            processing.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Data Tools S.A -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between mb-4">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ebony">Data Tools S.A</h3>
              <p class="text-xl text-red-orange">Test Analyst junior</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-gray-600 mt-2 md:mt-0">
              <p>January 2010 - December 2012 (3 years)</p>
              <p class="text-sm">Bogot√° D.C., Colombia</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Focused on manual testing for transportation and traffic violation
            management systems.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Secci√≥n de Contacto -->
      <div class="text-center mt-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ebony mb-4">Interested in working together?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
          I'm available for new projects and collaborations. Let's talk about your next project!
        </p>
        <ContactButton />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
